Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.74,0:01:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.96,0:01:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊跟我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.55,0:01:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.58,0:01:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.29,0:01:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次考试这问题会出吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.02,0:02:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有听吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.61,0:02:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样很伤脑筋耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.16,0:02:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了你今天很怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.14,0:02:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.56,0:02:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.53,0:02:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.65,0:02:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这问题跟我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.57,0:02:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.83,0:02:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.96,0:02:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好做啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.36,0:02:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.89,0:02:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.05,0:02:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.32,0:02:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗\N这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.76,0:02:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.58,0:02:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会出啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.35,0:03:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊干嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.21,0:03:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的话就出声啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很蠢耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.50,0:03:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚在洗澡啊\N带女朋友来要跟我说一声啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.28,0:03:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.74,0:03:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要不要吃看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.66,0:03:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢好像很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.33,0:03:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃吗\N请吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道合不合味口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.30,0:03:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很温柔的姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.87,0:03:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好教吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.73,0:03:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不会教吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.21,0:03:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.77,0:03:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易懂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不太会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.16,0:03:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是他教我\N找其他人教吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.82,0:03:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家现在爸妈不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.74,0:04:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为某些原因\N就只有我和姊姊在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.17,0:04:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实最近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情烦恼着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.60,0:04:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.06,0:04:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.15,0:04:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我当成炮友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.07,0:04:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都会勾引我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.34,0:05:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的炮友是\N喜欢内射的巨乳姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.60,0:06:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.53,0:06:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.66,0:06:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦遗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.04,0:06:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.33,0:06:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.46,0:06:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚起床了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.54,0:06:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会迟到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到房间要敲门啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲门了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你又没醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.71,0:07:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.08,0:07:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.72,0:07:16.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流出来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流出来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.87,0:07:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.28,0:07:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间有点臭喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.16,0:07:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.89,0:07:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错觉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.59,0:07:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.58,0:07:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊先出去不要迟到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.59,0:08:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了回想起来\N真是有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.22,0:08:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是梦遗\N而是被姊姊玩弄了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.37,0:09:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.48,0:09:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.49,0:09:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.20,0:09:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.27,0:09:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快就醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.64,0:09:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是一早就醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.15,0:09:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么有精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.07,0:10:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑中都想着姊姊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.30,0:10:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这样弄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.03,0:10:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不起床的话会迟到喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.59,0:10:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊叫醒你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.44,0:10:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都变热了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.78,0:11:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.90,0:11:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.62,0:11:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.63,0:11:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边都变热了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.32,0:11:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.20,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上的肉棒舔看看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有反应啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.39,0:12:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.32,0:12:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着也这么舒服啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多舒服一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.59,0:12:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样含着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.06,0:13:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽动着喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多含一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.47,0:13:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这手很闲喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.60,0:13:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.72,0:13:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊的胸部让你摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边摸胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.88,0:13:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.53,0:13:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搓揉胸部啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.34,0:14:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢被夹着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.32,0:14:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又变硬了喔比刚刚更硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.74,0:14:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样弄胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.00,0:14:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边弄边手淫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.46,0:14:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顶到乳头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.86,0:14:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.03,0:15:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边含着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢被舔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.48,0:15:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.98,0:15:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢胸部呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.79,0:15:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰抬高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.45,0:15:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.02,0:15:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夹着比较舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.71,0:15:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.32,0:15:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒被包住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑出来了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多弄一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢乳交吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.61,0:16:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夹住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.03,0:16:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这样摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.11,0:16:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样夹住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.89,0:16:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么想自己夹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.82,0:16:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.07,0:17:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.82,0:17:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢被夹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.30,0:17:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样夹住的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.10,0:17:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道肉棒硬了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都勃起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢胸部啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很舒服喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.52,0:17:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这样吧
